issue.title: [CF 1231] Maelstrom Maximum
issue.body:
What do you expect to happen? What happens instead?
The maximum for Maelstrom in TMW only goes up to 100.  It needs to go up to at least 150.

What version of TellMeWhen are you using? ("The latest" is not a version)
8.00
